{"translation":{"id":"zh_web","name":"和合本","shortName":"CUV","englishName":"Chinese Union Version","language":"zho","languageName":"繁體/简体中文"},"book":{"id":"PSA","translationId":"zh_web","name":"诗篇","commonName":"诗篇","title":"诗篇","order":19,"numberOfChapters":150},"chapter":{"number":133,"content":[{"type":"verse","number":1,"content":["看哪，弟兄和睦同住， 是何等美善，何等可喜！"]},{"type":"verse","number":2,"content":["这好比贵重的油浇在头上， 流到胡须， 就是亚伦的胡须， 又流到他衣袍的边缘；"]},{"type":"verse","number":3,"content":["又好比黑门的甘露， 降在锡安的山上； 因为在那里，耶和华赐下福分， 就是直到永远的生命。"]}]},"numberOfVerses":3}